### Design System (`css/style.css`)

#### [NEW] [style.css](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/Diya Pharma/css/style.css)

Global design tokens and base styles:

- **Colors**: Primary green palette `#0A6E3D`, `#0D8C4D`, `#2ECC71`; accent gold `#E8A317`; neutral grays; danger red; semantic success/warning/error
- **Typography**: Google Fonts — `Poppins` for headings, `Inter` for body; scale from 14px body to 48px hero headings
- **Spacing**: 8px grid system (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64, 96px)
- **Buttons**: 
  - `.btn-primary`: Green bg `#0A6E3D`, white text, 12px 32px padding, 8px radius, `transform: translateY(-2px)` on hover
  - `.btn-secondary`: White bg, green border, green text, filled on hover
  - `.btn-accent`: Gold bg for special CTAs
  - All buttons: `font-family: Poppins; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: all 0.3s ease`
- **Cards**: White bg, subtle box-shadow `0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)`, 12px radius, hover lift effect
- **Forms**: Consistent input styling with green focus borders
- **Navigation**: Sticky header with glassmorphism backdrop-blur

