### Responsive Design (`css/responsive.css`)

#### [NEW] [responsive.css](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/Diya Pharma/css/responsive.css)

| Breakpoint | Target |
|-----------|--------|
| `≤ 480px` | Small mobile |
| `≤ 768px` | Large mobile / small tablet |
| `≤ 1024px` | Tablet |
| `≤ 1280px` | Small desktop |
| `> 1280px` | Large desktop |

Key responsive behaviors:
- Hamburger menu on mobile
- Product grid collapses from 3→2→1 columns
- Filter sidebar becomes slide-out drawer on mobile
- Cart table becomes stacked cards on mobile
- Footer columns stack vertically

